{"tid":1234181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"襯事件處於膠著狀態 應該整定文宣同勇武紀錄","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:02:46.000Z","uid":106799,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"11f03e0eed76a6c71fd5fafc524352f3a8f1f00d","tid":1234181,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"無可否認香港人昨日的確顯示出團結 值得鼓舞 但係我地之後仲有面對更多惡法 依一刻可以做咩？ 小弟有以下略見：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 最重要：千萬不要被分化</span></span><br />\n歷史上分化係中共既拿手好戲，但係我地要同自己講，我地係受教育既香港人，有獨立思考能力，唔會咁易比人帶風向，我地點都唔篤灰唔割蓆，兄弟爬山，<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非勇武你可以比意見但唔好互屌</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 持續文宣 hold人心</span></span><br />\n文宣今次係做得特別好，整poster leaflet好快，出片出相出tee出埋長輩圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣亦應有前瞻性</span>，我地可以準備定黎緊準備預見既野 eg 71 人工島 etc.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 整理勇武抗爭資料+準備物資</span></span><br />\n經歷勝於一切，企前線中線既勇武69 612就吸收左唔少經歷，包括物資、通訊、裝備、策略、應對措施 etc. 我地應該襯依家整理番資料 <span style=\"color: red;\">最好整成一本69 612 大全</span>，比之後發生既示威衝突作參考"},{"pid":"fdcf5e1a45d5920af1bdcf7f99cf13fb11be4852","tid":1234181,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d7184f6c5c5ee788f2b791cbb48f8d13f798d4d","tid":1234181,"uid":45046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:25.000Z","msg":"唔想變雨傘2.0嘅入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234083</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2300763cfd258fb043def003e035a927b375a026","tid":1234181,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},